# Vendored third-party demo corpora: kept LOCAL only (avoid repo bloat and
# third-party licensing in-tree). Provenance is in each DEMO_SOURCE.md, and
# hawki's own scan output (hawki_report/) plus the novel-run evidence are kept.
demo/not-so-smart-contracts/*
!demo/not-so-smart-contracts/DEMO_SOURCE.md
!demo/not-so-smart-contracts/hawki_report
demo/damn-vulnerable-defi/*
!demo/damn-vulnerable-defi/DEMO_SOURCE.md
!demo/damn-vulnerable-defi/hawki_report
demo/pancake-smart-contracts/*
!demo/pancake-smart-contracts/DEMO_SOURCE.md
!demo/pancake-smart-contracts/hawki_report
demo/DeFiVulnLabs/*
!demo/DeFiVulnLabs/DEMO_SOURCE.md
!demo/DeFiVulnLabs/hawki_report
!demo/DeFiVulnLabs/deep_novel
